<style type="text/css">
	/* Sticky footer styles
	-------------------------------------------------- */
	html {
	  position: relative;
	  min-height: 100%;
	}
	body {
	  /* Margin bottom by footer height */
	  margin-bottom: 60px;
	}
	.footer {
	  position: absolute;
	  bottom: 0;
	  width: 100%;
	  background-color: #f5f5f5;
	}
	footer p {
	    margin: 10px 0 10px;
	}
</style>
<footer class="footer">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row">
			<div class=".col-md-8 .col-md-offset-2">
				<p>
					<button class="btn btn-default" type="button" disabled="disabled">
						<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-comment" aria-hidden="true"></span> Provide feedback
					</button>
					<button class="btn btn-warning" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#reportBug" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="reportBug">
						<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-exclamation-sign" aria-hidden="true"></span> Report bug
					</button>
					<a class="btn btn-default pull-right" type="button" href="mailto:jamie@fleek.in" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="If you've got something to say, why not just send me an old-fashioned email?">
						<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-envelope" aria-hidden="true"></span> Email the developer
					</a>
				</p>
				<div class="collapse" id="reportBug">
					<div class="well">
						<p>
							Well done! However trivial (or possibly major) the bug is, please fill in the form below providing as much detail as possible - how you discovered the issue, what browser you're using and anything else you think might be helpful in fixing the problem. I am truly grateful for your time.
						</p>
						<p>
						If the bug is better illustrated using pictures, you can send an email to <a href="mailto:bugs@fleek.in">bugs@fleek.in</a> and attach screenshots.
						</p>
						<form class="form" action="<%= @name %>/reportBug" method="post">
							<div class="form-group">
								<textarea class="form-control" rows="3" name="report" placeholder="Please provide as much information as you can..." required></textarea>
							</div>
							<button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">Submit</button>
						</form>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>